<plot>It is a heartfelt story centering on Tony, a petty thief, who meets a twelve year-old runaway boy in a mountain diner. Seeing himself in the boy, Tony tries to persuade the stubborn boy to return home, all the while avoiding the sheriff and the diner owner hot on his trail. Eventually, the two learn about each other's pain and the chance encounter brings unexpected cures to their wounded souls.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?239402</url></doc>
